      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just frustrating bc i've been reading online and some people say it's like there's something \"hidden\" happening under the surface that you can't see until it suddenly explodes. is there some kind of biological reason why it stays so stagnant and then all of a sudden it's doubling in size overnight? it feels so unpredictable.",
      "source": "evaluator"
